<h1><span style="color: #993300;"><strong>School Closure Information: </strong></span></h1>
<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong>In accordance with the Governor’s guidelines, Conservatory Lab Charter School is closed until Monday, May 4th</strong></span></p>
<div>
<hr>
</div>
<h2><b>School Communications Regarding Conservatory Lab Charter School’s Response to COVID 19</b></h2>
</div>
<div>
<ul>
<li>March 16, 2020: <a href="http://www.conservatorylab.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/03.16.20-School-Closure-Resources-for-Families.pdf">School Closure Resources for Families </a>
</li>
<li>March 14, 2020: <a href="http://www.conservatorylab.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/03.14.20-Updated-School-Closure-Information.pdf">Updated School Closure Information</a>
</li>
<li>March 13, 2020: <a href="http://www.conservatorylab.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/03.13.20-School-Closure-Notice-for-Families-FINAL.pdf">School Closure Notice for Families</a>
</li>
<li>March 12, 2020: <a href="http://www.conservatorylab.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/03.12.20-Update-for-Families-Regarding-COVID-19-Access-to-Carney-Hospital.pdf">Update for Families Regarding COVID-19 &amp; Access to Carney Hospital </a>
</li>
